To locate 2026 in the spiral, one checks that  
(2·22+1)²=45²=2025<2026≤47²=2209,  
so 2026 sits on the “23rd ring” at coordinates (x,y)=(23,–22).  Its eight neighbors lie at

(22,–23)=2208,  (23,–23)=2209,  (24,–23)=2210  
(22,–22)=2025,            (24,–22)=2211  
(22,–21)=1850,  (23,–21)=2027,  (24,–21)=2212  

Summing these eight gives  
2208+2209+2210 +2025+2211+1850+2027+2212 =16952.
